Key Trick

Unlike LeetCode 33, duplicates make it impossible to always identify the sorted half.

Handle duplicates first:

Your Approach

if (nums[mid] == nums[left]) {
    left++;
    continue;
}

Standard Approach

if (nums[left] == nums[mid] &&
    nums[mid] == nums[right]) {

    left++;
    right--;
}

After removing duplicates, solve it exactly like LeetCode 33.

